# 🧠 Linux Kernel Development Journey

This repo tracks my daily learning journey to master Linux kernel development, virtualization, and system-level security.

## 🗓️ Progress

| Day | Topic               | Description |
|-----|---------------------|-------------|
| 1   | Hello World Module  | Basic module with init and exit |
| 2   | Module Parameters   | Accepting user input with `module_param` |
| 3   | Timers              | Kernel timers with `timer_list` |
| ... | ...                 | ... |

 Each folder has its own `README.md`.
